    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、握手会はちゃんと出来たのかしら……",
      "startTime": 6.450000095367432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.995238113403321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、午前中は握手会お疲れ様\n……おーい、沙季？",
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.32857144673662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "午後のミニライブは、もっと人が増えるらしいし",
      "startTime": 18.328571446736657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりサニピの握手会の時\n私が横についていれば良かったかしら……",
      "startTime": 24.386457923737673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん、ダメ！　そんなの",
      "startTime": 27.31671202977499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、そろそろミニライブが始まるんだが",
      "startTime": 30.095736869176235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.09573686917626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "きゃっ！？ 　{user}さんっ！？",
      "startTime": 33.94573677380881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.07355988820392
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "女性のそばに音も立てずに忍び寄るなんて……\nマナー違反ですよ！",
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、何度か声をかけたんだけど\n沙季が気付かなかったんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 43.87358233133953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか……失礼しました\nもう私達の出番ですか？",
      "startTime": 50.28082381052276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、午後も予想以上にファンが\n集まってくれたみたいだ",
      "startTime": 54.981646388616326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.712422414315036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "それは嬉しいですね……",
      "startTime": 56.712422414315064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "浮かない顔だな……\n何か気になることでもあるのか？",
      "startTime": 61.49315053578946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.812422557366226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "実は……千紗のことがずっと心配で",
      "startTime": 63.81242255736623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.55872635413442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "午前中の握手会はちゃんと出来たのかな\nこのあとのミニライブは大丈夫かなって……",
      "startTime": 70.62567594752784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "握手会の会場も、月ストとサニピで別々だったしな\n千紗とは会ってないのか？",
      "startTime": 79.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.76081071380297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "はい、握手会が終わってからはまだ",
      "startTime": 80.76081071380297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.25355444434801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "……すみません、自分のグループじゃなくて\n妹のことばかり気にかけてしまって",
      "startTime": 87.24927117510161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "別に謝るようなことじゃないだろう？",
      "startTime": 90.14584455970449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.94121871474904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、私は月のテンペストのメンバーですから",
      "startTime": 92.94121871474904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "たとえ妹でも、同じ事務所でも\n競い合うライバルグループです",
      "startTime": 99.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.85307846549682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "それなら仕事では、月ストのメンバーを\n優先すべきだと思います……",
      "startTime": 104.8350659736349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、千紗に何もしてあげられない自分も\n凄くもどかしくて",
      "startTime": 110.21104060314985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ千紗の様子をこっそり見に行ってみるか",
      "startTime": 112.18230957491092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.93675393564365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "えっそんな、もうすぐライブですし\nみんなに迷惑じゃ……",
      "startTime": 119.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "少しなら大丈夫だろう。行ってみよう",
      "startTime": 120.9409750424422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.54097504244216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "あ、千紗……\n落ち込んでる……",
      "startTime": 128.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.8701813547125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私は千紗の近くにいた方が\n良かったんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 132.23684802137925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それじゃ千紗の成長にならないんじゃないかな",
      "startTime": 133.6905687249637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.05319909224275
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……そうですよね",
      "startTime": 138.05319909224275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、グループは違っても姉妹なのは変わらない\n沙季が千紗を心配するのは自然なことだよ",
      "startTime": 145.6938339627719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.88972131002058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_01_03-ski021.m4a",
